{"GYL57GfQwaP":{"id":"GYL57GfQwaP","type":"work","title":"藝林累百","authors":[{"name":"李紹文","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《藝林累百》·八卷","author_info":"明李紹文撰","summary":"明李紹文撰。紹文位元組之，華亭人。是編成於天啟癸亥。因《小學紺珠》而變其體例，摭拾故實，不分門類，不詳出處，但以數目為標題，自一至百，故名曰累百。大抵餖飣疏舛，不足以資考證也。","edition":"浙江吳玉墀家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":8}},"GYL57GoLSN3":{"id":"GYL57GoLSN3","type":"work","title":"庶物異名疏","authors":[{"name":"陳懋仁","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《庶物異名疏》·三十卷","author_info":"明陳懋仁撰","summary":"明陳懋仁撰。懋仁有《年號韻編》，已著錄。是編匯輯物名之異者，為之箋疏。凡二千四百五十二名，分二十五部。然多捃拾雜說，轉相稗販。如柔祇雪凝，圓靈水鏡，謝莊月賦，人人習讀，而其注稱類書地曰柔祇，是並《文選》未考也。大瀛海字出騶衍傳，而注曰大瀛海之異名見《楞嚴經注》，是並《史記》未考也。眢井字見《左傳》，而注曰韻書井無水曰眢，是三傳亦未考也。其他可以例見矣。又異名者，名之異者也。如虹一名挈貳，電一名列缺是也。而所列雞彝、黃目、瑞節、玉瓚之類乃其本名，何以為異？至於沙噀泥蟲乃是異物，並無別名，濫列簡牘，以充卷帙，體例亦乖舛之甚也。","edition":"浙江吳玉墀家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":30},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=5300919","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-chongzhenkeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY7240","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"崇禎刻本","version":"v10","total_page":1017,"paragraph_count":2255,"check_type":"AI整理"}},{"id":"shidianguji-chongzhenkeben-1","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02059378","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"崇禎刻本","version":"v3","total_page":969,"paragraph_count":7513,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL57GboM5R":{"id":"GYL57GboM5R","type":"work","title":"文竽匯氏","authors":[{"name":"傅作興","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《文竽匯氏》·二十四卷","author_info":"明傅作興撰","summary":"明傅作興撰。作興字廷用，建昌人。是書匯輯古來姓氏，兼載人物，分君姓、臣姓、諸侯、大夫、公族、補遺、覆姓，各標目上闌，而下附偶語一二聯，體例已陋。至所列系胄，皆妄以己意附會之。如以皇姓為出於三皇氏，胥姓為出於赫胥氏，桑姓為出於空桑氏，有若巢父為出於有巢氏，鑿空牽合，不可枚舉。非特昧於三代姓氏之辨，即後世譜牒諸家，亦全未寓目，可謂不知而作者矣。自序雲，文本於氏，正文者宜先正其氏以辨其文，而濫竽是懼，故以二字為名。其說亦支離無義理雲。","edition":"安徽巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":24},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=4299297","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-chongzhenkeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02059349","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"崇禎刻本","version":"v2","total_page":1819,"paragraph_count":18295,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL57GEzqH9":{"id":"GYL57GEzqH9","type":"work","title":"劉氏鴻書","authors":[{"name":"劉仲達","role":"編","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《劉氏鴻書》·一百八卷","author_info":"明劉仲達編","summary":"明劉仲達編。仲達字九逵，宣城人。是書分二十四類，又分子目二百六十有奇，事實詞章，相雜而載，每條皆注所出，較明人杜撰之書稍有依據。然大抵轉引類書，不盡出於本文，則亦稗販之學也。卷端題湯賓尹刪定，而李維楨序乃稱校讎與有力者，為李成白、謝少連，賓尹序中亦無一字及刪定事。蓋坊賈刊是書時，以仲達諸生，恐不見重，借名於賓尹耳。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":108},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=688398","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=4590543","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-2","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=2010450","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlikeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY7233","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆刻本","version":"v12","total_page":4938,"paragraph_count":37783,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL57GNvL4o":{"id":"GYL57GNvL4o","type":"work","title":"蟫史","authors":[{"name":"穆希文","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《蟫史》·十一卷","author_info":"明穆希文撰","summary":"明穆希文撰。希文有《說原》，已著錄。是書專記鳥獸事實，故以蟫名，分為羽蟲、毛蟲、鱗蟲、甲蟲、諸蟲五類。然蟫乃蠹魚之別目，非蟲之總名，制名殊謬，徵引亦多未賅。又中間所稱《蟫史》曰者，即其本書。乃雜廁古書之間，反若引用者然，於體例亦乖也。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":11},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/蟫史","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=952276","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=1026738","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-2","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=2668416","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-jiaqingwukeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02000682","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"嘉慶五年刻本","version":"v2","total_page":1306,"paragraph_count":9947,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL57G7pL8f":{"id":"GYL57G7pL8f","type":"work","title":"事典考略","authors":[{"name":"徐袍","role":"編","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《事典考略》·六卷","author_info":"明徐袍編","summary":"明徐袍編。袍字仲章，婺源人。是書采前代事蹟及先儒議論，分目凡八十有一。割裂經典，叢雜瑣碎，蓋兔園冊子也。","edition":"江蘇周厚堉家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":6}},"GYL57Gj5Dvo":{"id":"GYL57Gj5Dvo","type":"work","title":"十三經類語","authors":[{"name":"羅萬藻","role":"編","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《十三經類語》·十四卷","author_info":"舊本題明羅萬藻編","summary":"舊本題明羅萬藻編。萬藻字文止，江西人。天啟丁卯舉人。福王時官上杭縣知縣。唐王僣號於福建，擢為禮部主事。未幾卒。故至今時文家稱曰羅儀部，《明史·文苑傳》附見艾南英傳中。是書因坊本《五經類語》，更取十三經廣之，分一百三十四類，杭州魯民重又為之注。案萬藻雖僅以時文名家，而所學具有原本，其時文幽渺湛深，純以意運，亦決不用此餖飣之功。況其時張溥與張采立複社，艾南英與章世純陳際泰及萬藻立豫章社，會南英選刻時文，塗乙過當，為眾所詬。乃取己及三人之文亦分合作、摘謬二例，塗乙其半，刊以示公。溥等因以離間其交，世純，際泰皆為所動，而萬藻恬於名譽，獨不從溥。今此書之首乃有溥序，與當日情事尤為乖刺。殆民重托稱萬藻，籍豫章社之名以行，又偽撰溥序，藉複社之名以取重。總之，坊賈伎倆而已。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":14},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=3980169","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-chongzhenshisanjinch","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/JDLS0218","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"崇禎十三年（1640）金閶東觀閣臣古齋刊本","version":"v1","total_page":1428,"paragraph_count":5043,"check_type":"粗校"}},{"id":"shidianguji-kangxiwushiwupanyulo","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/HY7231","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"康熙五十五年(1716)潘育龍弘遠堂刻本","version":"v4","total_page":1258,"paragraph_count":9443,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL57GXY8eB":{"id":"GYL57GXY8eB","type":"work","title":"五侯鯖","authors":[{"name":"彭儼","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《五侯鯖》·十二卷","author_info":"明彭儼撰","summary":"明彭儼撰。儼字若思，江西人。其書分類隸事，凡十四門。所載皆不著出典，摭拾叢雜，無可採錄。","edition":"兩江總督采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":12},"resources":[{"id":"shidianguji-kanben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/NA06710","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"刊本(序刊)","version":"v8","total_page":695,"paragraph_count":5343,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL57GBRvdd":{"id":"GYL57GBRvdd","type":"work","title":"故事選要","authors":[{"name":"王思義","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《故事選要》·十四卷","author_info":"明王思義撰","summary":"明王思義撰。思義有《宋史纂要》，已著錄。是書采擇子史故事，分類編次，凡十五門。多不注所出，動輒舛誤。如雪門收絳雪丹事，已為不倫；又訛張雲容為趙容雲，則他可知矣。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":14}},"GYL57GvUFf5":{"id":"GYL57GvUFf5","type":"work","title":"詩學匯選","authors":[{"name":"胡文煥","role":"編","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《詩學匯選》·二卷","author_info":"明胡文煥編","summary":"明胡文煥編。文煥有《文會堂琴譜》，已著錄。是書即坊本《詩學大成》中采輯重編，凡三十九門。所錄詩自六朝至於明代，妍媸並列，殊為猥雜。文煥自序，文亦陋劣。《詩學大成》本依託於李攀龍，此更掇拾其殘賸，風益下矣。","edition":"內府藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":2}},"GYL57G4J7Lb":{"id":"GYL57G4J7Lb","type":"work","title":"史學璧珠","authors":[{"name":"錢應充","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《史學璧珠》·十八卷","author_info":"明錢應充撰","summary":"明錢應充撰。應充字子美，紹興人。萬曆中貢生。是書分類隸事，以坊本綱鑒為主，而稍摭類書附益之。皆集為偶句，以便剽襲。冠以歷代帝王歌括，中分天地、災祥、君道、臣道、倫理、品論、吏部、戶部、禮部、兵部、刑部、工部、人身、德惡、人事、官職、物類十七門，又分子目三百二十五。如以心學屬之禮部，不知其何取。又品論門中有何如一目，尤從古類書所未聞。自序言書成之日，夢一神人，襆頭皂袍，自稱待制包某，以其褒貶合義，特來勞之。又言作序之日，五星聚奎。語皆謬妄，即其書可知也。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":18}},"GYL57GTGvCw":{"id":"GYL57GTGvCw","type":"work","title":"婦女雙名記","authors":[{"name":"李肇亨","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《婦女雙名記》·一卷","author_info":"明李肇亨撰","summary":"明李肇亨撰。肇亨字會泰，嘉興人。太僕卿日華之子也。所錄古今婦女雙名凡六十七人。自序謂王元美《弇州卮言》、張睿父《琅琊代醉編》、陳無功《析醒漫錄》中皆有所載，而彼此未備。暇日偶有所睹，即隨手錄出，又兼三書考其出處雲。","edition":"編修程晉芳家藏本"}],"juan_count":{"number":1},"resources":[{"id":"wikisource","name":"维基文库","url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/婦女雙名記","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=87005","type":"text"}]},"GYL57Gz5rA3":{"id":"GYL57Gz5rA3","type":"work","title":"文奇豹斑","authors":[{"name":"陳繼儒","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《文奇豹斑》·十二卷","author_info":"明陳繼儒撰","summary":"明陳繼儒撰。繼儒有《邵康節外記》，已著錄。是編分天文、地理、人物、文史、花木、鳥獸、器用、人事、釋教、字學十類，皆剽竊餖飣之文。末一卷分韻編古字，尤多舛謬。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":12},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=2813289","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-shenshengekeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02059413","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"申申閣刻本","version":"v4","total_page":816,"paragraph_count":4765,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL57GJZjvf":{"id":"GYL57GJZjvf","type":"work","title":"儒函數類","authors":[{"name":"汪宗姬","role":"撰","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《儒函數類》·六十二卷","author_info":"明汪宗姬撰","summary":"明汪宗姬撰。宗姬字肇邰，歙縣人，是書《明史·藝文志》作《儒數類函》，蓋刊本誤也。所錄故實皆以數統計，自一至萬，罔不畢具。然體例冗雜。如二獻條下乃列二齊等諡二十二條，如但據標目，於何尋檢？且名曰儒函，當詳於儒，而二氏之言仍複采入甚？至萬善二字引及太上感應篇，不亦傎乎？","edition":"安徽巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":62},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=5634282","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-wanlisishiwangyoulon","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02059317","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"萬曆四十年汪猶龍刻本","version":"v6","total_page":1909,"paragraph_count":3599,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true},"GYL57Grx2s1":{"id":"GYL57Grx2s1","type":"work","title":"尚友錄","authors":[{"name":"廖用賢","role":"編","dynasty":"明"}],"indexed_by":[{"source":"欽定四庫全書總目","source_bid":"GY4HvsY3w3u","title_info":"《尚友錄》·二十二卷","author_info":"明廖用賢編","summary":"明廖用賢編。用賢字賓于，建寧人。是書成於天啟中。蒐采古人事實，以韻為綱，以姓為目，其例一如《萬姓統譜》。諸所紀載，詳略失宜，無所考證，蓋亦為應俗作也。","edition":"浙江巡撫采進本"}],"juan_count":{"number":22},"resources":[{"id":"ctext","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=252775","type":"text"},{"id":"ctext-1","name":"CText","url":"https://ctext.org/wiki.pl?if=gb&res=635606","type":"text"},{"id":"shidianguji-tianqikeben","name":"识典古籍","url":"https://www.shidianguji.com/book/CADAL02059391","type":"text+image","metadata":{"edition":"天啓刻本","version":"v3","total_page":2433,"paragraph_count":17258,"check_type":"AI整理"}}],"has_text":true,"has_image":true}}